quran[18]{c,v,t}:
  52,32,"Kaa ko haqqille ma…ď…ďe …óeen yamir…ďe …óuum? Kaa hara ko …ďe yim…ďe bew…ďe tan?"
  52,33,"Kaa …ďe mbi'ay won'de : "O sincu nde?" Si ko woni, wonaa …ďe gooŇč…óinoo…ďe."
  52,34,"Yoo …ďe ngaddu yeewtere sugu mayre, si wonii ko …ďe gooŇč…óu…ďe."
  52,35,"Kaa …ďe tagira …ďaawo tak…óo? Kaa ko kam…ďe ngoni tagoo…ďe …ďen?"
  52,36,"Kaa (ko) kam…ďe tagi kammuuji …óin e leydi ndin? Ko woni kon, …ďe njananaaka."
  52,37,"Kaa …ďe njogiti ngaluuji Joomi maa …óiin? Kaa ko kam…ďe ngoni hu…ďindii…ďe …ďeen?"
  52,38,"Kaa …ďe njogiti …ďargal ngal …ďe njentorta? yoo ke…óitii…óo e ma…ď…ďe oon addu hujja …ďanngu…óo !"
  52,39,"Maa ko …ďi…ó…ďe rew…ďe ngoodanta mo, onon kam wor…ďe …ďeen?"
  52,40,"Kaa a la…ďndi …ďe njo…ďdi, hara jo…ďugol ndi no teddani …ďe?"
  52,41,"Kaa …ďe nganndu fii wirnii…ói …óiin, hara he…ďe mbinnda?"
  52,42,"Maa …ďe paala fewjoore? ko yeddu…ďe …ďeen, woni fooletee…ďe pewje …ďen."
  52,43,"Kaa he…ďe mari dewetee…óo ko woori Allah? Senaare woodanii Allah, e kon ko …ďe cirkata !"
  52,44,"Si …ďe nji'ii ta∆īatine immornde ka kammu no yani, …ďe mbi'a: "Ko duule pawondir…óe"."
  52,45,"Terto …ďe, haa …ďe kawroya e √Īalaande ma…ď…ďe nde …ďe leptoytee e mum;"
  52,46,"√Ďande nde pewje ma…ď…ďe duncanoytaa …ďe hay hu'unde, …ďe ngonaa kadi walloytee…ďe."
  52,47,"Ko pellet, hino woodani too√Ī…ďe …ďeen, lepte goo ko wonaa …óen …óon. Ko ko …ďuri …óuu…óude kon e ma…ď…ďe, …ďe nganndaa."
  52,48,"Mu√Ī√Īo √Īaawoore Joomi maa ndeen. Tawde pellet, ha…óa e ndenka amen. Seniniraa yettugol Joomi maa, tuma …ďaŇčoto…óaa."
  52,49,"Jehma on kadi, subbunhinano…óaa mo e ka mutugol koode."